From: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:11:23 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] selftests/damon/drgn_dump_damon_status: support failed region
 quota charge ratio

Extend drgn_dump_damon_status.py to dump DAMON internal state for DAMOS
action failed regions DAMOS quota charge ratio, to be able to write new
selftests

Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 tools/testing/selftests/damon/drgn_dump_damon_status.py | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/tools/testing/selftests/damon/drgn_dump_damon_status.py b/tools/testing/selftests/damon/drgn_dump_damon_status.py
index 5b90eb8e7ef8..972948e6215f 100755
--- a/tools/testing/selftests/damon/drgn_dump_damon_status.py
+++ b/tools/testing/selftests/damon/drgn_dump_damon_status.py
@@ -112,6 +112,8 @@ def damos_quota_to_dict(quota):
         ['goals', damos_quota_goals_to_list],
         ['goal_tuner', int],
         ['esz', int],
+        ['fail_charge_num', int],
+        ['fail_charge_denom', int],
         ['weight_sz', int],
         ['weight_nr_accesses', int],
         ['weight_age', int],
